name: VOXELFINE #10: "David" by Michaelangelo 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: This is my second sculpture Voxelfine. It's the closest I'm going to get to #dickspo in this project. It was a pretty fun, straight-forward build overall! Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
